info.name: Chibi Maruko-chan
info.description: Chibi Maruko-chan is a shōjo manga series written and illustrated by Momoko Sakura. The series depicts the simple, everyday life of Momoko Sakura, a young girl everyone calls Maruko, and her family in suburban Japan in the year 1974.

moreInfo.japanese: ちびまる子ちゃん, Little Maruko-chan, Petite Maruko-chan
